## ⛳ Completion signal — REQUIRED LAST LINE (run_claude_job.sh reads this for Steve's Telegram alert)

After all work and logging, the VERY LAST line of your output MUST be exactly one of:
- `ROUTINE_COMPLETE` — the canon-reviewer ran AND (it drafted ≥1 grounded proposal that is now surfaced OR it correctly wrote none). A no-op month IS complete.
- `ROUTINE_INCOMPLETE: <one-line reason>` — the canon-reviewer could not read the signal sources (blocked-*), the --list enumeration failed, or the Telegram push failed when proposals existed.

Output nothing after that line.
